creator: Agrobazaar Online
descriptionHtml:
AgroBazaar Online offers a fast, safe and convenient e-commerce platform, where our merchant offer thousands of unique, new and genuine items in various categories such as processed food, fisheries, agriculture, livestock and agro-tourism.

AgroBazaar Online is owned by Ministry of Agriculture & Agro-based Industries and managed by Federal Agricultural Marketing Authority (FAMA).

Buyer can shop in online agriculture ecosystem truly made by Malaysian for global market.

AgroBazaar offers:

EASY ITEM SEARCH
Search and select from a variety of agro-based products, e-books, shops, services and even agro-based homestay from 100% genuine Malaysian sellers.

FAST BROWSING
View and browse the latest shops, special offers, popular orders, top sales and recommended products and services.

MULTI-CATEGORY SELECTION
Browse fresh produce and agro-based category selection menu to view all the latest products and services.

PROMO/EVENT NOTIFICATIONS
Receive notifications on announcements, promotions, events and product reviews.

EXCLUSIVE VOUCHERS
Receive and apply special cash or gift vouchers for your purchases.

EASY PURCHASE
Quick buy via QR code feature.

NEARBY SHOP SUGGESTIONS
View nearby seller shops based on your GPS location.

BUYER’S MENU
View, edit and manage your orders, reviews, enquiries and wish lists.
descriptionShort: Enjoy fast and easy shopping of Malaysia’s fresh produce and Agro-based products
